## Notes / Addons / corrections

* Install-script: Better way to init conda for your shell: `cd ~ && wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && chmod +x Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && ./Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p $PWD/conda && eval "$($PWD/conda/bin/conda shell.bash hook)" && SHELLNAME=$(/bin/ps -p $$ | grep -oE '[^ ]+$' | tail -1) && conda init $SHELLNAME `
